{
  "stem": "27.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I belonged there, and we went every summer to a-- like boy scout camp, you know, with the-- kind-- we had a uniform, the kind of uniform, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to boy scout camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was there about for six weeks every year, you know, summer, when school was out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father was-- my family was strictly orthodox, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they retained a real kosher house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father told me-- and he traveled a lot, because he had to go to Prague, to Budapest, to Vienna, and all over, you know, for business.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only thing I ate is eggs and toast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what he told me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Coffee, naturally, I drink in moderation, because I don't eat what's not kosher.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if I went to somewhere-- and-- but he was a moderate Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my grandfather had beard from here to here-- my grandfather, you know what mean?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was only moderate, you know what I mean-- no facial hair or anything, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- well taken children, you know what I mean-- well brought up-- very little problem.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't cause no problem-- and just a normal, good life, a normal good life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no reason for any type-- he was not political.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His political affiliation-- was he was a Social Democrat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Czechoslovakia, there were two major parties, actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were many small ones-- I think four or five-- were Agrarian and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were Social Democrats and National Democrats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most Jewish people belonged to the middle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was that was a middle of the road party-- Social Democrat-- you know what I mean-- which was similar here to the Democratic, even the Republican Party.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because it was not-- it wasn't a real liberal.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
